query:
SELECT d.id, d.valorTotal, d.mesServico, ts.nome as tipoServico 
FROM despesas d 
INNER JOIN tipos_servico ts ON d.tipoServicoId = ts.id 
WHERE MONTH(d.mesServico) = 12 AND YEAR(d.mesServico) = 2025
ORDER BY d.mesServico DESC
LIMIT 20
